    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/94aa30ae75b8c7c6a9c64ab05bd5dda7_4149738097179537059.png",
                "key": "溯因反繹法",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "溯因反繹法"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">琢光鏡</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">琢光鏡</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p>角色造成的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>變為<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">角色普通攻擊後：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素傷害</span>。如果此技能為<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">重擊</span>，則使此狀態的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合：2</span>（可疊加，最多疊加到3回合）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/8491b6dd997a8a4878767f1191a2b6aa_1798599905839921095.png",
                "key": "共相·理式摹寫",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "共相·理式摹寫"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素傷害</span>；消耗<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">琢光鏡</span>，此傷害提升所消耗<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">琢光鏡</span>的持續回合值。</p><p>如果消耗<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">琢光鏡</span>的持續回合為0/1/2，則為角色附屬持續回合為3/2/1的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">琢光鏡</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/a3b3108e0046cb101533a3bf6dcbe717_6936049462313027054.png",
                "key": "殊境·顯像縛結",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "殊境·顯像縛結"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span>」</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_5580748803283876664.png",
                "key": "草元素傷害‧其一",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "草元素傷害‧其一"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\"><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_6757280448119562979.png",
                "key": "草元素傷害‧其二",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_1632051201984006484.png",
                "title": "草元素傷害‧其二"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">重擊</span></strong></p><p>我方行動開始前，如果元素骰總數為偶數，則進行的「普通攻擊」將被視為「重擊」。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合結束階段，<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_186086010007009875.png",
